    • getValidationMessages

      public List<ValidationMessage> getValidationMessages() throws SBOLGraphException
      Gets a list validation messages corresponding to errors and best practices. A Validation message is of the following format:

      String message; URI property; Object invalidValue; Identified childEntity; ValidationMessage childMessage; ADD THE ABOVE TO THE VALIDATIONMESSAGE CLASS, do similar for all other class definitions.

      Specified by:
